/*!
\page usecode Using ROCS in Your Code

If CMake is used as a build system for your application, add the following code to CMakeLists.txt:
\code
find_package(ROCS)
if (NOT ROCS_FOUND)
	message(FATAL_ERROR "ROCS not found!")
endif (NOT ROCS_FOUND)
\endcode

\n
In order for your application to find ROCS, you have to define the environmental variable ${ROCS_DIR} pointig to the directory where ROCS is installed.

*/

